INSERT INTO
    trip_positions (
    trip_id,latitude,longitude,timestamp,course_over_ground,speed,navigation_status_id,rate_of_turn,true_heading,distance_to_shore,position_type_id,pruned_by
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$3::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$4::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$5::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$6::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$7::INT[],$8::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$9::INT[],$10::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$11::INT[],$12::INT[]
    )
